Home


Random cheatsheets for things I keep forgetting


Commands




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.


mkdocs gh-deploy
 - deploy changes to github.
